    <string name="sources_title">Text sources</string>
    <string name="sources_text">All texts are public domain: Westminster Leningrad Codex; Byzantine Textform 2018 (Robinson–Pierpont); Wycliffe; Tyndale; Geneva 1599; KJV with Apocrypha; Webster Bible 1833; Bible Martin 1744; Lutherbibel 1545; Reina-Valera 1909; Bíblia Livre (Almeida, TR); Елизаветинская Библия 1757; Синодальный перевод. Webster\'s American Dictionary of the English Language (1828) via the 1828.mshaffer.com digitization. Strong\'s Concordance (1890/1894) dictionary © Open Scriptures, CC-BY-SA. Hebrew morphology © Open Scriptures (CC-BY); Greek parsing by Maurice A. Robinson (public domain). Cross-references © openbible.info, CC-BY. App text data via scrollmapper, thiagobodruk and byztxt projects. Background music: Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com), CC BY 4.0.</string>
